Ecommerce Search Cleanser

Usign python NLTK we are able to extract the following data from a sentence:
- Brands
- Merchants
- Price
- Description of the product such as color 

So if a person types in "I want a blue dress for 50 dollars", the cleanser will pick out the needed information such as blue, dress, and 50.
With that it will relate the content to correct assignement for search purposes. 
